<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV64">
<l>niṉṟatentai yūrakatti runtatentai pāṭakat</l>
<l>taṉṟuveḵka ṇaikkiṭanta teṉṉilāta muṉṉelā</l>
<l>maṉṟunāṉpi ṟantilēṉpi ṟantapiṉma ṟantilēṉ</l>
<l>niṉṟatum miruntatumki ṭantatummeṉ neñcuḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My Father standing in Ūrakam, my Father sitting in Pāṭakam,</l>
<l>[His] reclining in Veḵkaṇai on that day was all before, when I did not exist!</l>
<l>I was not born then, I have not forgotten after being born:</l>
<l>[His] standing, sitting, and reclining are inside my heart!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
